{"word":"ὑπερίσταμαι","slug":"ὑπερίσταμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερίσταμαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>:— <i>to stand over</i> another, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>to stand over</i> one <i>for protection, protect</i>, <el>τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}